'''溪李'''（{{lang-xm|Prunus rivularis}}；{{lang-en|creek plum}}）是[[薔薇科|薔薇科]][[李屬|李屬]]落葉灌木，為[[美國|美國]]特有植物。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Plants Profile for ''Prunus rivularis'' (creek plum)|url=https://plants.usda.gov/core/profile?symbol=PRRI|accessdate=2021-03-06|author=USDA, NRCS|work=The PLANTS Database|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126182612/https://plants.usda.gov/core/profile?symbol=PRRI|dead-url=no}}</ref>種加詞{{lang|la|''rivularis''}}是指在溪流附近。'''雁李'''（{{lang-xm|Prunus munsoniana}}；{{lang-en|wild goose plum}}）有時被認為和溪李是同一個種，但雁李為灌木或小喬木，<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Plants Profile for ''Prunus munsoniana'' (wild goose plum)|url=https://plants.usda.gov/core/profile?symbol=PRMU|accessdate=2021-03-06|author=USDA, NRCS|work=The PLANTS Database|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126193009/https://plants.usda.gov/core/profile?symbol=PRMU|dead-url=no}}</ref>可高達6~9米，果實更大且更適合食用。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Plum Potential in the Bluegrass: a Fantasy Rooted in Reality|url=http://bluegrasswoodland.com/uploads/Prunus_munsoniana.pdf|accessdate=2021-03-06|author=Julian Campbell|date=2017|work=bluegrasswoodland.com|archive-date=2019-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726213959/http://bluegrasswoodland.com/uploads/Prunus_munsoniana.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>狹義的溪李分佈於[[科羅拉多|科羅拉多]]、[[堪薩斯|堪薩斯]]、[[俄克拉荷馬|俄克拉荷馬]]、[[阿肯色|阿肯色]]、[[德克薩斯|德克薩斯]]，<ref name=":0" />而雁李分佈於[[堪薩斯|堪薩斯]]、[[俄克拉荷馬|俄克拉荷馬]]、[[阿肯色|阿肯色]]、[[德克薩斯|德克薩斯]]以及[[美國東南部|美國東南部]]。<ref name=":1" />

